These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-1::.
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: ambient, classical
2 different games are played: scrabble, canasta
There are 2 different favourite colors: ivory, orange
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: biathlon, cycling
1. the person who's sport is biathlon is not to the right of the person playing canasta##8
2. the person playing canasta is somewhere to the left of the person who likes ivory##5
3. the fan of ambient is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |
| Music-Genre      | classical     | ambient      |
| Game          | canasta | scrabble    |
| Color         | orange   | ivory |
| Sport   | biathlon  | cycling      |

