.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-8-2::.
There 2 different types of food: pear, onion
2 different games are played: backgammon, bridge
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: montecristo, baccarat
House: modern, cape-cod
1. the person eating onion is on the far right##1
2. the person playing backgammon is somewhere to the left of the montecristo-smoker##5
3. the baccarat-smoker is not to the right of the montecristo-smoker##8
4. the modern house is not the person playing bridge##6

.:: Answer ::.
|             |         1          |      2      |
| Food    | pear        | onion    |
| Game       | backgammon         | bridge |
| Cigar         | baccarat | montecristo   |
| House   | modern               | cape-cod  |

