2. the game-smoker is not to the right of the person playing billiard##8
3. the person driving the bike is somewhere to the left of the person who likes turquise##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |
| Color   | coral       | turquise |
| Transport   | bike       | van    |
| Cigar   | aristoff | game |
| Game           | whist        | billiard   |

