1. the dunhill-smoker is somewhere to the right of the person who likes ebony##5
2. the owner of the frog is not to the left of the person who growsdahlia##8
3. the person who growsdahlia is on the left of the owner of the frog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |
